data.description: Welcome to the Bel Aire Estates property! Freshly painted and remodeled Home is a definite must see! This is a gorgeous 3 bedroom plus bonus room for office, workout or craft room, 2 Bath and 2 car garage. Home features an open floor concept from the kitchen onto the dining area and family room equipped with gas fireplace.  The kitchen entails gorgeous quartz countertops, stove/oven, dishwasher with self-closing cupboards and drawers! Escape into the spacious Master Bedroom and bathroom with a walk-in closet! The front yard landscaping features new grass with automated sprinkler system for your front and backyard.  As you walk through the back doors you can entertain your guest under the covered patio and stay cool either by sitting under the lighted ceiling fanlights or by taking a dip in the sparkling lighted pool! Home is in a well-established part of Dinuba and close to Walmart shopping center, Ridge Creek Golf Course, Schools and a community park! Contact your real estate agent for a personal showing!
